#include<iostream>
#include<cstdlib>

using namespace std;

int max(int a,int b){
  if(a>b) return a;
  else return b;
}

int min(int a,int b){
  if(a<b) return a;
  else return b;
}

int main(){
  int x[2][2],y[2][2];
  int xsou,xeou,ysou,yeou,t;
  cin>>t;
  while(t--){
    cin>>x[0][0]>>y[0][0]>>x[0][1]>>y[0][1];
    cin>>x[1][0]>>y[1][0]>>x[1][1]>>y[1][1];
    xsou=-1; xeou=-1; ysou=-1; yeou=-1;
    if (x[1][0]<=x[0][1] && y[1][0]<=y[0][1] && x[1][1]>=x[0][0] && y[1][1]>=y[0][0]){
      xsou=max(x[0][0],x[1][0]);
      ysou=max(y[0][0],y[1][0]);
      xeou=min(x[0][1],x[1][1]);
      yeou=min(y[0][1],y[1][1]);
    }
    if (xeou!=1 && yeou!=-1 && xsou!=-1 && ysou!=-1) cout<<xsou<<" "<<ysou<<" "<<xeou<<" "<<yeou<<"\n";
    else cout<<"No Overlap\n";
  }
}
